@CleanArc.WebApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Login as manager
POST {{CleanArc.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "manager",
  "password": "Manager123!"
}

### Create service request (anonymous)
POST {{CleanArc.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/service-requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "citizenName": "Yael Cohen",
  "description": "Large pothole near bike lane causing dangerous swerves.",
  "category": 2,
  "street": "Dizengoff 201",
  "cityArea": "Center",
  "affectsSensitivePopulation": true
}

### List open requests (requires token)
GET {{CleanArc.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/service-requests/open
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Dashboard (manager role)
GET {{CleanArc.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/service-requests/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
